column16: Mike McCoy doubles (3) on a fly ball to right fielder David DeJesus.   Travis Snider to 3rd.
Jose Molina lines out to left fielder Mitch Maier.
Travis Snider singles on a fly ball to center fielder Rick Ankiel.
Jose Bautista homers (3) on a fly ball to left field.   Lyle Overbay scores.
Vernon Wells pops out to shortstop Yuniesky Betancourt in foul territory.
Adam Lind grounds out, shortstop Yuniesky Betancourt to first baseman Billy Butler.
Magglio Ordonez grounds into a force out, third baseman Alberto Callaspo to second baseman Chris Getz.    Don Kelly out at 2nd.
Don Kelly grounds into a force out, first baseman Billy Butler to catcher Jason Kendall.    Gerald Laird out at home.    Ramon Santiago to 3rd.    Austin Jackson to 2nd.    Don Kelly to 1st.
Austin Jackson walks.    Gerald Laird to 3rd.    Ramon Santiago to 2nd.
Dustin Pedroia homers (2) on a fly ball to left field.   Jacoby Ellsbury scores.
Jacoby Ellsbury singles on a soft line drive to left fielder Scott Podsednik.
Marco Scutaro flies out to right fielder David DeJesus.
Jason Varitek homers (2) on a fly ball to right field.
Mike Cameron pops out to second baseman Chris Getz.
Johnny Damon grounds out sharply, pitcher Luis Mendoza to first baseman Billy Butler.
Austin Jackson doubles (3) on a line drive to center fielder Rick Ankiel.    Adam Everett scores.  Austin Jackson advances to 3rd, on fielding error by center fielder Rick Ankiel.
Adam Everett doubles (1) on a ground ball to left fielder Scott Podsednik.
Gerald Laird bunt grounds out, third baseman Alberto Callaspo to first baseman Billy Butler.
Brandon Inge grounds out, shortstop Yuniesky Betancourt to first baseman Billy Butler.
Carlos Guillen flies out to left fielder Scott Podsednik.
Miguel Cabrera homers (2) on a fly ball to right field.    Johnny Damon scores.    Magglio Ordonez scores.
Magglio Ordonez singles on a ground ball to shortstop Yuniesky Betancourt.    Johnny Damon to 2nd.
